title: Aziraphale Attempts To Avert The Apocalypse By Possessing Madame Tracy | Good Omens | Prime Video
author: Amazon Prime Video UK
comment: Props to Madame Tracy for only slightly freaking out at Aziraphale's sudden appearance
Aziraphale is such an adorable cinnamon roll that he even makes possession cute!
THANK YOU AMAZON FOR KEEPING THE FANDOM ALIVE
Props to Miranda Richardson for this performance. Masterpiece.
This actress is phenomenal! I’ll have to look her up on IMDB. To play multiple characters so distinctly takes serious acting skill.
description:
In the first recorded case of Angelic possession, Aziraphale takes over Madame Tracy's body and lets a woman speak to her rather grumpy dead husband.
